This project enforces a strict 7-phase development lifecycle.
Before writing ANY code, read: docs/methodology/README.md

The 7 phases: PRD → Architecture → Technical Spec → Task Breakdown → Test Spec → Implementation → Review & Deploy

KEY RULES:
- No code without a Technical Spec (docs/methodology/templates/03-technical-spec.md)
- No implementation without tests (write test skeletons first)
- Code must match the Technical Spec exactly
- If the spec is wrong, fix the spec first, then fix the code

Templates: docs/methodology/templates/

Project: Gradience Protocol — peer-to-peer capability settlement for AI Agents
Tech: Solana (Anchor/Rust), TypeScript SDK, Cloudflare Workers, Next.js
Core doc: protocol/WHITEPAPER.md
Architecture: protocol/design/
